{"tid":1525960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可以搞黨鐵方法同其他資料","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:35:45.000Z","uid":191555,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fff8f83839258e5781d0363dd85f8c5f1ee0a7ea","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"原本想寫本MTR逃走手冊，但真係無乜地方可以行同走，所以改為其他資訊。<br />\n<br />\n十字鎖匙 （於深水涉鴨記/淘寶/五金舖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQBOH3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQBOH3T.png&h=d82957a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用於開啟通往月台兩邊進入路軌的門<br />\n<br />\n打開車廂內既緊急handle 開車門用<br />\n<br />\n用於鎖住車門<br />\n<br />\nReset 車上的緊急通話系統<br />\n<br />\nB6 / C6匙 （需要由mtr員工或曾於mtr進行工程作的人員私下配鎖匙流出）<br />\n進入mtr站部份房間的鎖匙<br />\n<br />\n列車不可行駛情況<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下當車廂有人拉緊急聯絡掣（拉Pad）<br />\n月台上有人按緊急停車掣 （打Pep）<br />\n或月台員工於玻璃房內打了緊急停車掣 (打Ess(站長室都有，一般站員打左掣，站長室都要打)）<br />\n<br />\n一般要列車行駛都需要reset各個緊急掣先可以開車<br />\n<br />\n但有例外情況<br />\n<br />\n車長有一個手動模式可以慢駛<br />\n<br />\n或者車頭有裝置可以令車不受限於車站緊急掣按正常速度離開<br />\n<br />\n以上皆為參考<br />\n<br />\n我唔建議大家挾持車長或者進入路軌逃生<br />\n但必要時可以爆入車長駕駛倉去㩒掣去關上車門<br />\n哩個係無辦法既辦法，但請大家唔好傷害任何職員。<br />\n<br />\n唔建議大家入路軌係因為路軌比較黑同埋難行，同埋有好多危險地方，而且狗一樣有機會落路軌到時都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家對黨鐵實有不滿，短期內都唔會搭佢<br />\n大家唔搭一樣可以搞鳩佢<br />\n要搞佢除左不合作運動：<br />\n1）阻車門幕門<br />\n2）拉PED<br />\n3)  打PEP<br />\n之外<br />\n可以掉d易燃物品落路軌<br />\n恐嚇港鐵報稱擺放左爆炸品（可以撚埋狗）<br />\n虛報比港鐵知路軌上有人/動物/物件<br />\n掉野去架空電欖（最好可以Q住/掛係上面）<br />\n甚至令到電欖斷/爆<br />\n哩各項大家都容易做到<br />\n<br />\n最後重申多次<br />\n希望你地唔好搞前線職員（入面有藍有黃）<br />\n因為他地根本話唔到事<br />\n<br />\n要搞就搞九龍灣總部高層<br />\n或者青衣既車務控制中心（OCC）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個會發夢的不專業MTR staff上<br />\n<br />\n如果同事有方法或者補充都可以同其他人補充下可行方法"},{"pid":"4d8a781f914daf8664e831fee86796a0bae30b0e","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4b588688574defbbc81ac5d959d5f30aabf0b","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b73f2a994b35d67f1bf8ebc1f77f1eaf582741f","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef61a507508bbdc2b02e59a50751af0e6985430","tid":1525960,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae5e3c7f7458ed5cde0140dcaff91e417212ea5","tid":1525960,"uid":8812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d26e078445087ab4dca16dffb2d4dbc2230d8e2","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9460f895398f6c5a37ad3071a6ab923d54f26b7","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47237a763fe8a0948abc981cc29742e1ca7026b","tid":1525960,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EBV7z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EBV7z0.jpg&h=04974a70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmbZPOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmbZPOm.jpg&h=3895b2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E75zDGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE75zDGG.jpg&h=74538fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zSY5mH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zSY5mH.jpg&h=dc026972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkJA7z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkJA7z2.jpg&h=f98bffcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe1c4eb6ff2038006a5e5ccd716f0e2310c6a8aa","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588ff894509ea10c7f06b63a10f4264fabb9c361","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1d15fb7a1a76669f12f20c4393e0e3cad28948","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa7df439fb5984d14615f9e77698285ae1d8b23","tid":1525960,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"58a8ba15ba59a4c2d32af362ed54e98a50ad924b","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"毋忘831"},{"pid":"64ba2829b8718cdf5db0e2cbcf2c285437236973","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"隨便搞黨鐵"},{"pid":"e1ebac32bccbbb5aed3a999f96118c93ec952d7a","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"黨鐵可恥"},{"pid":"4de4e316a7738d2d728a354470b102f880658558","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"M你老母TR"},{"pid":"0efb8143d513b4106279cccc3edde03d37eb63c8","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706c5b131d517a2c98f797e19f1ac01f751165a8","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母黨鐵"},{"pid":"4e33ed6f864178c22719bbb1298131dae0957ce3","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"有冇其他師兄提供方法搞黨鐵？"},{"pid":"94c5d3343e054d01f44b2d950681c09a5155b5bd","tid":1525960,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"純轉貼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxSVnvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjxSVnvV.jpg&h=ef93a5c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeJ12xs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeJ12xs.jpg&h=863334c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=720iJqChtxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D720iJqChtxM&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=28b32871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=720iJqChtxM</a><br />\n有巴打建議大家千其唔好咁做，有樣野叫澎脹發泡膠，五金鋪賣一支40蚊左右，送支管，隊支管塞入面噴啲膠入去，之後啲膠就會喺入面<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">澎脹50倍同變硬</span></strong>，用過就知澎脹得勁快而且勁難清得乾淨，乜機都打柴啦。"},{"pid":"c97a7b933b48835af1ce00434c58b48616fd34c6","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"ac389261c24c3bae642ed9666bc94d7ba78881d8","tid":1525960,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"唔搞黨鐵唔係人"},{"pid":